WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:03.566
Son, look at his wife

2
00:00:03.766 --> 00:00:04.900
It's too much.

3
00:00:04.900 --> 00:00:07.400
If he seriously injures our spirit axe again

4
00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:08.600
I'll go even further.

5
00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:09.900
You treat your mother-in-law like this

6
00:00:09.900 --> 00:00:11.300
You are going to be struck by lightning

7
00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:13.166
Being struck by lightning is disrespectful

8
00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:14.033
Open mouth

9
00:00:14.066 --> 00:00:15.266
It's you who should be struck by lightning

10
00:00:15.266 --> 00:00:16.600
I'll say it again.

11
00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:18.800
If he seriously injures our spirit axe again

12
00:00:18.866 --> 00:00:19.833
I promise.

13
00:00:19.866 --> 00:00:22.666
Let your Song family not see the sun tomorrow

14
00:00:23.100 --> 00:00:25.166
No, keep going like this

15
00:00:25.166 --> 00:00:26.333
If he really divorced me

16
00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:28.300
I won't get a penny

17
00:00:28.866 --> 00:00:29.666
Mom

18
00:00:30.466 --> 00:00:31.966
Apologize to Miss Lin Yi

19
00:00:34.966 --> 00:00:38.900
Changjing, mother worked hard to raise you

20
00:00:38.966 --> 00:00:40.566
That's how you treat your mother

21
00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:43.000
You really want to ruin your son's future

22
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:44.266
I am a talisman

23
00:00:44.266 --> 00:00:46.333
Can he starve to death without our Song family?

24
00:00:46.333 --> 00:00:48.866
Then if it wasn't for the beggar, you wouldn't apologize again

25
00:00:48.966 --> 00:00:50.833
I cut off the mother-son relationship with you

